{
  "id": "doubao-batch-asr",
  "name": "Doubao Batch ASR",
  "version": "0.3.0",
  "registration_url": "",
  "description": "## Usage\n\n1. **Create an application**: create an app in the [legacy console](https://console.volcengine.com/speech/service/9), enable the video caption service, then copy the APPID and Access Token.\n2. **Configure the plugin**: enter the Access Token in the API Key field and the APPID in the APPID field.",
  "api_key_label": "Access Token",
  "localized": {
    "zh": {
      "description": "## 使用流程\n\n1. **创建应用**：在[旧版控制台](https://console.volcengine.com/speech/service/9)创建应用并开通视频字幕服务，获取 APPID 和 Access Token。\n2. **配置插件**：在 Omni Code 中 API Key 字段填入 Access Token，APPID 字段填入应用标识。"
    }
  },
  "setting_fields": [
    {
      "key": "model",
      "label": "APPID",
      "help": "Application ID from the Volcengine legacy console.",
      "placeholder": "your_appid",
      "required": true,
      "localized": {
        "zh": {
          "help": "火山引擎旧版控制台的应用标识。"
        }
      },
      "capabilities": ["speech.batch_asr"]
    },
    {
      "key": "resource_id",
      "label": "Language",
      "help": "Recognition language. Defaults to zh-CN.",
      "placeholder": "zh-CN",
      "required": false,
      "localized": {
        "zh": {
          "label": "语种",
          "help": "识别语种，默认 zh-CN。"
        }
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "zh-CN",
          "label": "Mandarin Chinese",
          "localized": { "zh": { "label": "中文普通话" } }
        },
        {
          "value": "yue",
          "label": "Cantonese",
          "localized": { "zh": { "label": "粤语" } }
        },
        {
          "value": "en-US",
          "label": "English",
          "localized": { "zh": { "label": "英语" } }
        },
        {
          "value": "ja-JP",
          "label": "Japanese",
          "localized": { "zh": { "label": "日语" } }
        },
        {
          "value": "ko-KR",
          "label": "Korean",
          "localized": { "zh": { "label": "韩语" } }
        }
      ],
      "capabilities": ["speech.batch_asr"]
    }
  ],
  "capabilities": ["speech.batch_asr"],
  "capability_configs": {
    "speech.batch_asr": {
      "base_url": "https://openspeech.bytedance.com",
      "auth_header": "Authorization",
      "auth_scheme": "Bearer;",
      "path": "/api/v1/vc/submit?appid=${model}&language=${language}&use_itn=True&max_lines=1&words_per_line=15",
      "poll_path": "/api/v1/vc/query?appid=${model}&id=${task_id}",
      "request_content_type": "audio/wav",
      "response_text_path": "utterances.0.text"
    }
  }
}
